<h3>Allowable Expenses</h3>
<p><em>@_run-name_@</em></p>

<p>
Set the radio button to 'percentage' if you want to allow a proportion (1=all 0=none) of that item. Set to flat-rate if you
want to set a maximum amount instead, and enter the maximum (p.a.) in the box on the right.
</p>
<table>
<tr><th></th><th>Flat Rate or Proportional?</th><th>Proportion or absolute amount allowable</th></tr>

<tr class="tableRowEven"><td align="right">Travel Expenses</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-travel_expenses-is_flat_@</td>
<td>@_allowable_expenses-travel_expenses-amount_@</td></tr>

<tr class="tableRowOdd"><td align="right">Pension</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-pension-is_flat_@</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-pension-amount_@</td></tr>

<tr class="tableRowEven"><td align="right">avcs</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-avcs-is_flat_@</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-avcs-amount_@</td></tr>

<tr class="tableRowOdd"><td align="right">Union Fees</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-union_fees-is_flat_@</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-union_fees-amount_@</td></tr>

<tr class="tableRowEven"><td align="right">Child Care</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-childMinding-is_flat_@</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-childMinding-amount_@</td></tr>

<tr class="tableRowOdd"><td align="right">Friendly Socs</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-friendly_societies-is_flat_@</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-friendly_societies-amount_@</td></tr>

<tr class="tableRowEven"><td align="right">Sports</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-sports-is_flat_@</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-sports-amount_@</td></tr>

<tr class="tableRowOdd"><td align="right">Loan Repayments</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-loan_repayments-is_flat_@</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-loan_repayments-amount_@</td></tr>

<tr class="tableRowEven"><td align="right">Medical Insurance</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-medical_insurance-is_flat_@</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-medical_insurance-amount_@</td></tr>

<tr class="tableRowOdd"><td align="right">Charities</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-charities-is_flat_@</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-charities-amount_@</td></tr>

<tr class="tableRowEven"><td align="right">Maintenance Payments</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-maintenance_payments-is_flat_@</td><td>@_allowable_expenses-maintenance_payments-amount_@</td></tr>
